<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>Clipper City Market</title>
	<meta name="description" content="<%= content_for?(:description) ? yield(:description) : "Bringing together Baltimoreâ€™s most creative chefs and food purveyors for a weekend pop-up market with a full lineup of culinary workshops and demos." %>">
